Data understanding

Data understanding#

Data Understanding adalah proses mendalami data: struktur, sumber, kualitas, distribusi, dan keterbatasannya. Tujuannya memastikan data layak dipakai untuk analisis & modelling.

  1. Langkah-langkah Umum

  • Ingest & sampling ‚Äî ambil sample dataset (mis. 1k baris) untuk eksplorasi awal.

  • Profiling ‚Äî statistik dasar: count, unique, min/max, mean, std, percentiles.

  • Visualisasi awal ‚Äî hist, boxplot, scatter untuk deteksi pola & outlier.

  • Quality checks ‚Äî missing, duplicates, inconsistent formats, range checks.

  • Data dictionary / metadata ‚Äî jelaskan tiap kolom: tipe, allowed values, deskripsi.

  • Lineage & source validation ‚Äî darimana data? apakah ETL mengubahnya?

  • Privacy & compliance ‚Äî PII handling, GDPR/PDPA bila relevan.

  1. Dimensi Kualitas Data (detail)

  • Completeness (kelengkapan): ada missing/null?

  • Accuracy (ketepatan): apakah nilai mewakili kenyataan? (sulit verifikasi tanpa sumber eksternal)

  • Consistency (konsistensi): format kolom konsisten (tanggal, kode pos), business rules konsisten (ShipDate >= OrderDate)

  • Uniqueness: duplicate transactions / order IDs

  • Validity: apakah nilai di domain yang valid (mis. Segment ‚àà {Consumer, Corporate, Home Office})

  • Timeliness: data up-to-date sesuai kebutuhan analisis

  • Integrity / Referential: relasi antar tabel (jika ada) valid

  1. Data Dictionary (contoh ringkas untuk Superstore)

  • Order ID ‚Äî string, unik per order (mis. CA-2018-‚Ä¶)

  • Order Date ‚Äî date, format (YYYY-MM-DD)

  • Ship Date ‚Äî date

  • Ship Mode ‚Äî categorical (First Class, Second Class, Standard Class, Same Day)

  • Sales ‚Äî numeric (float), total sale amount

  • Quantity ‚Äî integer

  • Discount ‚Äî numeric (0.0 - 1.0) biasanya percent

  • Profit ‚Äî numeric (float)

  1. Praktik EDA & Pemeriksaan Kualitas

# === 3. Load env & koneksi ke Supabase PostgreSQL ===
import psycopg2
from dotenv import load_dotenv
import pandas as pd
from google.colab import files

load_dotenv()

USER = os.getenv("USER")
PASSWORD = os.getenv("PASSWORD")
HOST = os.getenv("HOST")
PORT = os.getenv("PORT")
DBNAME = os.getenv("DBNAME")

try:
    conn = psycopg2.connect(
        user=USER,
        password=PASSWORD,
        host=HOST,
        port=PORT,
        dbname=DBNAME
    )
    print("‚úÖ Connection successful!")
except Exception as e:
    print("‚ùå Failed to connect:", e)

# === 4. Upload CSV ke Colab ===
uploaded = files.upload()   # pilih file Sample - Superstore.csv

# baca CSV dengan encoding latin1 (umum untuk file dari Excel/Windows)
df = pd.read_csv("Sample - Superstore.csv", encoding="latin1")
print("Preview data:")
print(df.head())

# === 5. Buat tabel di PostgreSQL jika belum ada ===
cursor = conn.cursor()

create_table_query = """
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS superstore (
    Row_ID INT,
    Order_ID VARCHAR(50),
    Order_Date DATE,
    Ship_Date DATE,
    Ship_Mode VARCHAR(50),
    Customer_ID VARCHAR(50),
    Customer_Name VARCHAR(100),
    Segment VARCHAR(50),
    Country VARCHAR(50),
    City VARCHAR(50),
    State VARCHAR(50),
    Postal_Code VARCHAR(20),
    Region VARCHAR(50),
    Product_ID VARCHAR(50),
    Category VARCHAR(50),
    Sub_Category VARCHAR(50),
    Product_Name VARCHAR(255),
    Sales FLOAT,
    Quantity INT,
    Discount FLOAT,
    Profit FLOAT
);
"""
cursor.execute(create_table_query)
conn.commit()
print("‚úÖ Table ready!")

# === 6. Insert data CSV ke PostgreSQL ===
for _, row in df.iterrows():
    cursor.execute("""
        INSERT INTO superstore (
            Row_ID, Order_ID, Order_Date, Ship_Date, Ship_Mode,
            Customer_ID, Customer_Name, Segment, Country, City,
            State, Postal_Code, Region, Product_ID, Category,
            Sub_Category, Product_Name, Sales, Quantity, Discount, Profit
        )
        VALUES (%s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s)
    """, tuple(row))

conn.commit()
print("‚úÖ Data inserted to Supabase!")

# === 7. Cek apakah data berhasil masuk ===
cursor.execute("SELECT COUNT(*) FROM superstore;")
print("üìä Total rows in table:", cursor.fetchone()[0])

cursor.close()
conn.close()
print("üîí Connection closed.")

print(df.dtypes)

# === 5. Kualitas data ===

## 5a. Outlier Analysis (IQR) untuk kolom numerik
def detect_outliers_iqr(data, col):
    Q1 = data[col].quantile(0.25)
    Q3 = data[col].quantile(0.75)
    IQR = Q3 - Q1
    lower = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR
    upper = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR
    outliers = data[(data[col] < lower) | (data[col] > upper)]
    return outliers

print("\nüîé Outlier pada kolom Sales:")
outliers_sales = detect_outliers_iqr(df, "Sales")
print(outliers_sales[["Row_ID", "Sales"]].head())

print("\nüîé Outlier pada kolom Profit:")
outliers_profit = detect_outliers_iqr(df, "Profit")
print(outliers_profit[["Row_ID", "Profit"]].head())

## 5b. Konsistensi data (contoh: Postal_Code harus numerik)
inconsistent_postal = df[~df["Postal_Code"].astype(str).str.isnumeric()]
print("\nüö® Data tidak konsisten pada Postal_Code:")
print(inconsistent_postal.head())

## 5c. Missing Values
print("\nüîé Jumlah missing values per kolom:")
print(df.isnull().sum())

## 5d. Duplikasi Data
print("\nüîé Jumlah data duplikat:", df.duplicated().sum())

# === 6. Ringkasan Statistik ===
print("\nüìä Ringkasan Statistik Numerik:")
print(df.describe())

import psycopg2

USER = os.getenv("USER")
PASSWORD = os.getenv("PASSWORD")
HOST = os.getenv("HOST")
PORT = os.getenv("PORT")
DBNAME = os.getenv("DBNAME")

try:
    conn = psycopg2.connect(
        user=USER,
        password=PASSWORD,
        host=HOST,
        port=PORT,
        dbname=DBNAME
    )
    print("‚úÖ Connection successful!")
except Exception as e:
    print("‚ùå Failed to connect:", e)
    # Keluar dari skrip jika koneksi gagal
    exit()

# === 4. Upload CSV ke Colab ===
# Pastikan file iris-full.csv sudah diunggah ke Colab
print("Silakan unggah file 'iris-full.csv' Anda.")
uploaded = files.upload()

# Baca CSV dengan encoding utf-8 (umum)
try:
    df = pd.read_csv("iris-full.csv", encoding="utf-8")
except UnicodeDecodeError:
    # Coba encoding lain jika gagal
    df = pd.read_csv("iris-full.csv", encoding="latin1")

# Ubah nama kolom agar tidak ada spasi
df.columns = df.columns.str.replace(" ", "_").str.lower()

print("Preview data:")
print(df.head())
print("\nNama kolom yang akan digunakan:")
print(df.columns)
print("\nTipe data per kolom:")
print(df.dtypes)

# === 5. Buat tabel di PostgreSQL jika belum ada ===
cursor = conn.cursor()

create_table_query = """
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS iris (
    id INT,
    class VARCHAR(50),
    sepal_length FLOAT,
    sepal_width FLOAT,
    petal_length FLOAT,
    petal_width FLOAT
);
"""
cursor.execute(create_table_query)
conn.commit()
print("\n‚úÖ Tabel 'iris' berhasil dibuat atau sudah ada!")

# === 6. Insert data CSV ke PostgreSQL ===
# Hapus semua data di tabel terlebih dahulu untuk menghindari duplikasi
cursor.execute("DELETE FROM iris;")
conn.commit()
print("‚úÖ Data lama di tabel 'iris' telah dihapus.")

for _, row in df.iterrows():
    cursor.execute("""
        INSERT INTO iris (
            id, class, sepal_length, sepal_width, petal_length, petal_width
        )
        VALUES (%s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s)
    """, tuple(row))

conn.commit()
print("‚úÖ Data 'iris' berhasil diunggah ke Supabase!")

# === 7. Cek apakah data berhasil masuk ===
cursor.execute("SELECT COUNT(*) FROM iris;")
print("\nüìä Total baris dalam tabel 'iris':", cursor.fetchone()[0])

cursor.close()
conn.close()

# === 1. Import library yang dibutuhkan ===
# Pastikan library psycopg2 dan pandas sudah terinstal di lingkungan Python Power BI
import psycopg2
import pandas as pd

# === 2. Buat fungsi untuk koneksi dan mengambil data ===
def get_data_from_supabase(table_name):
    """
    Menghubungkan ke database Supabase dan mengambil data dari tabel yang ditentukan.
    """
    # === 3. Atur kredensial Supabase Anda di sini ===
    # Ubah nilai di bawah ini dengan kredensial dari file .env Anda
    # HATI-HATI: Jangan bagikan kredensial ini!
    USER = "postgres.wzdudprybyachqxjhmpw"
    PASSWORD = "ks9unws6dHe76WJD"
    HOST = "aws-1-us-east-2.pooler.supabase.com"
    PORT = "5432"
    DBNAME = "postgres"

    try:
        # Buat koneksi ke database
        conn = psycopg2.connect(
            user=USER,
            password=PASSWORD,
            host=HOST,
            port=PORT,
            dbname=DBNAME
        )

        # Buat query SQL
        query = f"SELECT * FROM {table_name};"

        # Gunakan pandas untuk membaca data langsung dari SQL
        df = pd.read_sql(query, conn)

        print("‚úÖ Data berhasil diambil!")
        return df

    except Exception as e:
        print("‚ùå Gagal terhubung atau mengambil data:", e)
        return None

    finally:
        # Tutup koneksi
        if 'conn' in locals() and conn:
            conn.close()
            print("üîí Koneksi ditutup.")

# === 4. Jalankan fungsi dan ambil data ===
# Ganti nama tabel di bawah ini ('iris' atau 'superstore') sesuai kebutuhan Anda
df_iris = get_data_from_supabase('iris')

# Cek apakah data berhasil diambil sebelum ditampilkan
if df_iris is not None:
    # Tampilkan DataFrame (Power BI akan membaca output ini)
    print("\nBerikut preview 5 baris pertama dari data:")
    print(df_iris.head())

    # KODE INI AKAN DIKEMBALIKAN KE POWER BI
    df = df_iris

# Copy dataset dari Power BI
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.neighbors import LocalOutlierFactor
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA

# Copy dataset Power BI
dataset = dataset.copy()

# Pilih fitur numerik
X = dataset[['petal length', 'petal width', 'sepal_length', 'sepal_width']]

# KNN Outlier Detection (LOF)
lof = LocalOutlierFactor(n_neighbors=20, contamination=0.05)  # contamination=5% dianggap outlier
y_pred = lof.fit_predict(X)

# Tambah kolom hasil ke dataset
dataset['outlier'] = y_pred  # -1 = outlier, 1 = normal

# PCA untuk visualisasi
pca = PCA(n_components=2)
X_pca = pca.fit_transform(X)

plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
plt.scatter(
    X_pca[:,0],
    X_pca[:,1],
    c=dataset['outlier'],
    cmap='coolwarm',
    edgecolor='k'
)
plt.xlabel("PCA 1")
plt.ylabel("PCA 2")
plt.title("Outlier Detection dengan KNN (LOF)")
plt.show()

# The following code to create a dataframe and remove duplicated rows is always executed and acts as a preamble for your script:

# dataset = pandas.DataFrame(petal length, petal width, sepal_length, sepal_width)
# dataset = dataset.drop_duplicates()

# Paste or type your script code here:
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA

# Copy dataset dari Power BI
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA

# Copy dataset dari Power BI
dataset = dataset.copy()

# Pilih fitur (pakai semua fitur kalau sudah ada di dataset)
X = dataset[['petal length', 'petal width', 'sepal_length', 'sepal_width']]

# K-Means clustering (3 cluster)
kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=3, random_state=42, n_init=10)
dataset['cluster'] = kmeans.fit_predict(X)

# PCA untuk reduksi dimensi ke 2D
pca = PCA(n_components=2)
X_pca = pca.fit_transform(X)
dataset['pca1'] = X_pca[:, 0]
dataset['pca2'] = X_pca[:, 1]

# Plot
plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
plt.scatter(
    dataset['pca1'],
    dataset['pca2'],
    c=dataset['cluster'],
    cmap='viridis',
    edgecolor='k'
)
plt.xlabel("PCA 1")
plt.ylabel("PCA 2")
plt.title("Clustering Iris dengan K-Means")
plt.show()
